verbose_text: The results of Begg 's and Egger 's tests revealed that no publication biases existed in terms of the comparison of serum IL-6 levels in HCC and healthy control groups (XREF_FIG), the comparison of serum IL-6 levels in cirrhosis and healthy control groups (XREF_FIG), the comparison of serum IL-6 levels in hepatitis and healthy control groups (XREF_FIG), the comparison of serum IL-6 levels in cirrhosis and HCC groups (XREF_FIG) and the comparison of serum IL-6 levels in hepatitis and healthy control groups (XREF_FIG).
